     <div type="poem">
   <head>Ad Anglum Lectorem.</head>
   <l>SCire cupis mores hominum, lustrareque terras?</l>
   <l>hic depicta tibi cuncta viaere <gap reason="illegible" resp="#pdcc" extent="1 letter">
         <desc>•</desc>
      </gap>ice<gap reason="illegible" resp="#pdcc" extent="1 letter">
         <desc>•</desc>
      </gap>.</l>
   <l>Ne Linguae ignotae exaniment, hunc consule nostrum</l>
   <l>Atlantem: notus sic tibi mundus erit.</l>
   <l>Orbem fulcit <hi>Atlas,</hi> opus hoc intellige: Atlantem</l>
   <l>Lector, &amp; Atlantis non leve fulcis onus.</l>
   <closer>
      <signed>R. B. S. Hosp.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
